headline: Amazon Is Spending Billions to Win Christmas. Why the Stock Looks Like a Bargain.
summary: Amazon is pouring colossal amounts of money into delivery, robots, and artificial intelligence. In the near term, the company expects to boost its holiday market share. In the longer term, it’ll be the recipient of a torrent of free cash flow.
